    <item>
      <title>Essence of Scrum: Daily Scrum</title>
      <link>//william-yeh.net/post/2020/08/daily-scrum-in-a-nutshell/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Aug 2020 16:00:00 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>//william-yeh.net/post/2020/08/daily-scrum-in-a-nutshell/</guid>
      <description>This article discusses the essence of Daily Scrum .
In a nutshell Daily Scrum is a time-boxed daily event in which the Developers gather together to quickly inspect current performance and to identify necessary actions in order to increase the confidence in achieving the Sprint Goal .
Output Essential:
Updated confidence in the Sprint Goal supported by evidence.
Updated plans, if necessary, for achieving the Sprint Goal .
